snippet.textDisplay: There is something about this song. It’s quite normal for your brain to get tired of listening to something again and again because of neural fatigue, hence what’s astonishing is that this track here is just as fresh for me to listen to 10 times a day as it was 2 years ago. Not one song has remotely been close to having been as long in my playlist. Or in my head for that matter. This is a masterpiece, which deserves way more recognition around the world. This is perfect music, which has something magical about it, something that goes beyond reason.
